      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Goblins of Golarion pg. 12</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> 1 sp; <strong>Weight</strong> 1 lb.<br/><strong>Category</strong> Tools</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbolN.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"Only legal goblin PCs are allowed to choose anything from this book\"/>Description</h2><p>A fire carrier is a conical device made of thickly insulated leather and wood designed to carry a live coal under a layer of ash. A fire carrier can keep a coal red hot for 24 hours and allows anyone to light a fire in normal conditions without having to resort to Survival checks, alchemical devices, or magic. </p>",
